description:
It's premiere week for The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City! The ladies our bringing it with a season 2 debut episodes that has a bit of everything, FBI arrests, the aunt who smells like hospital, a Mary podcast, a new Housewife, Heather referencing Apres Ski, and so much more! After RHOSLC, Danny recaps The Real Housewives of Potomac, which had a Surry County tourist video that will live in my head forever, and lots more! Finally, Danny shares a detour about a squirrel in Ohio and some TV recommendations.


RHOP: 33:00ish


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
